task.summary:
Added a vector map of Nodes. Every map has at the border unwalkable nodes, so if your map world is 10x10 will be stored a 12x12. This helps for add the neighbours of every nodes (8 for everyone) except for the border's nodes, they are neighbours but they don't have them. SO the alhorithms can take 8 neighbours for every walkable nodes.
We have now to generate a map..
Map can be draw now. Next step: auto resize
